::Aerotaur::
    "I don't know.  I guess I'm not terribly hungry.  Hmm ah I need to know 
why do you hate Maximals so much?"  After saying this he stops and turns back 
to flying centaur mode.  He reaches behind him and puts Trinity down in front 
of him.  He looks down and smiles.  Seeing her makes him wonder how long it 
has been since he last smiled.
